    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. Hemolysis index predictions demonstrate agreement with FDA interlaboratory experimental data across all five operating points. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Submission proceeds to 510(k) predicate comparison.",
